      "content": "hey, i was watching the markets today and i felt this really weird sharp pressure in my chest right before that tech stock dipped. i've noticed this happening a lot lately. like, my body literally reacts to the volatility before the charts even show it. do u think there's any way my nervous system is picking up on the algo patterns?",
